00:07:47.860 --> 00:07:52.090
fuels. It's a completely different
chemical in fact. If somebody gives you a

00:07:52.090 --> 00:07:59.340
hard time about the fact that the CO2
changes slightly after the temperature,

00:07:59.340 --> 00:08:04.590
you can tell them that's expected because
