00:08:22.130 --> 00:08:28.100
warming which is false. The fact is that
ice ages are ended by the changes in the

00:08:28.100 --> 00:08:30.670
earth's orbit as you heard earlier today.

00:08:30.670 --> 00:08:35.020
So it's not surprising that the
temperature changes first and you can

00:08:35.020 --> 00:08:41.130
think of CO2 as a feedback that amplifies
