00:08:41.130 --> 00:08:49.670
It's not actually a huge increase. It's
maybe two degrees bigger of a change than

00:08:49.670 --> 00:08:55.560
you would have gotten otherwise. So humans
are adding CO2 directly to the atmosphere

00:08:55.560 --> 00:08:59.830
and so ice ages are not a good analog,
it's a red herring.

00:08:59.830 --> 00:09:05.040
I couldn't resist showing this because
